      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "docs: improve plugin inventory layout",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Replace the generated plugin inventory table with plain Markdown list entries so wrapping is scoped to each plugin instead of shared table columns.\n- Add a blank line between generated entries and drop the raw `Surface:` field from the inventory page.\n- Keep `/plugins/reference` as a short generated landing page, delete the generated Parallel reference stub, and link the Parallel inventory entry directly to its existing setup doc.\n\n## User Intent\nJosh asked for a KISS docs fix that makes the plugin inventory readable on normal screens, stays coherent with existing generated docs conventions, avoids a custom HTML layout unless Markdown is not viable, avoids duplicate inventory/reference content, avoids AI/frontmatter disclosure churn, removes dense/sloppy generated fields, deletes the random Parallel stub page, and includes before/after visual proof.\n\n## Visual Proof\nScreenshots were captured from the synced `openclaw/docs` static shell at the plugin inventory section.\n\n| Width | Before | After |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| 390px | ![Before 390px](https://tmpfiles.org/dl/wLwdKoVstNpw/before-mobile-390.png) | ![After 390px](https://tmpfiles.org/dl/wxwVKTVaX1wZ/after-mobile-390.png) |\n| 768px | ![Before 768px](https://tmpfiles.org/dl/wOwNKNVoXcAO/before-tablet-768.png) | ![After 768px](https://tmpfiles.org/dl/w5wsKSVTXMeO/after-tablet-768.png) |\n| 1120px | ![Before 1120px](https://tmpfiles.org/dl/w5wfKHV7XElN/before-desktop-1120.png) | ![After 1120px](https://tmpfiles.org/dl/wLwHKKVaXEg3/after-desktop-1120.png) |\n\nFinal rendered preview metrics at 390px, 768px, and 1120px: `tableCount=0`, `overflowCount=0`, no `Surface:` label, and the Parallel inventory entry links to `/tools/parallel-search`.\n\n## Verification\n- `node scripts/generate-plugin-inventory-doc.mjs --check`\n- `git diff --check origin/main..HEAD`\n- `nix shell nixpkgs#oxfmt --command oxfmt --check scripts/generate-plugin-inventory-doc.mjs docs/plugins/plugin-inventory.md docs/plugins/reference.md docs/.i18n/glossary.zh-CN.json`\n- `node scripts/check-docs-mdx.mjs`\n- `node scripts/check-docs-i18n-glossary.mjs --base origin/main`\n- `node scripts/docs-link-audit.mjs`\n- `nix shell nixpkgs#pnpm --command pnpm dlx --config.resolution-mode=highest markdownlint-cli2 --config config/markdownlint-cli2.jsonc docs/plugins/plugin-inventory.md docs/plugins/reference.md`\n- `nix shell nixpkgs#pnpm --command pnpm docs:list`\n- `openclaw/docs`: `npm run docs:build:shell`\n- `openclaw/docs`: `npm run docs:smoke:shell`\n",
